{"tid":1278604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推!!快啲登記!!!] 【選民登記今截止】選舉處僅暫收14萬新登記 辦事處開放至凌晨收表","createTime":"2019-07-02T13:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:43:36.000Z","uid":85713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"864507408d529604afbcee4346a7ec6d4274e589","tid":1278604,"uid":85713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"新一個選民登記周期申請今日（7月2日）結束，選舉事務處指截至今日上午，於2019年選民登記周期，已完成處理約14萬2,000宗新登記選民申請，正點算近日收到的申請表格數量。按照慣例，選舉處將於稍後時間，公佈今年的新登記選民最終數字。對上一次區議會選舉、即2015年，共有26.2萬新登記選民；2016年的立法會選舉，該年則有17.7萬新登記。<br />\n<br />\n選舉處指，今日經電郵及傳真收到大量新登記選民申請，傳真線路或較繁忙。該處提醒巿民，公眾如經電郵發送選民登記申請表格，請留意郵箱是否收到處方電郵伺服器自動發出的確認通知，如未有收到確認通知，需重新發送電郵，或以其他方式送交申請表格，但提交新登記申請的法定限期為今日：「只要有關表格於法定限期前、即7月2日或之前，成功送達上述選舉事務處辦事處或伺服器，選舉事務處便會處理有關申請。 」意味着假如今日才寄出，其登記將不獲受理。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》致電選舉處熱線，職員指位於九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓的辦事處會開放至今晚11時59分，接收市民親身遞交的選民申請。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【登記做選民 7月2日截止】<br />\n<br />\n網上登記：<br />\n。方法1（登入此網站 ，按步驟3分鐘完成）<br />\n。方法2（可用手機登入，在選舉事務處網頁打開REO-1表格，使用免費手機應用程式Adobe Fill &amp; Sign打開表格，再按指示填寫資料，按儲存文件並以點擊分享，再電郵至 form@reo.gov.hk）<br />\n<br />\n詳情可參閱選舉事務處網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=f9c718e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7146035e39fa195ca7707edcf02f02a3a9f89879","tid":1278604,"uid":85713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:18:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d486c20ce44a713f454e07fa7d3bec99a839ed2d","tid":1278604,"uid":85713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:18:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d6e7f466e910f565fc624665ad93b52e5e76184","tid":1278604,"uid":85713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3a205f81cf2c6158f8c7825a825f58a6637224e0","tid":1278604,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"推 最後今日呀 懲罰佢老母！！！"},{"pid":"e9e6d15bfb0b87c4b572180ecc645c7b21a92d53","tid":1278604,"uid":124894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=f5973fff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/</a><br />\n試下呢個"},{"pid":"e48b10e406c9d5f719076f02c505a815673e77b4","tid":1278604,"uid":85713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"⼁乛⼀⼀⼀⼂<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3ds2HV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3ds2HV.png&h=7aa6137f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下佢個撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快啲登記啊!!!!!!"},{"pid":"5468c2db266042054f2adcd5315248347ed0d982","tid":1278604,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"860925dfc820a446320e8b7c5d816a1971a2d703","tid":1278604,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26dfe67f2ddff7c343540061528375bd6d51a4be","tid":1278604,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span s